OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,FThe South West's ambulance service
OL,7,Frecorded its busiest day on record on
OL,8,FTuesday 26 May, as the UK heatwave
OL,9,Framped up demand.
OL,11,FSouth Western Ambulance Service NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust (SWASFT) crews
OL,13,Fresponded to almost 4,000 incidents
OL,14,Facross the region.
OL,16,FThe service is asking people across
OL,17,Fthe South West to protect themselves
OL,18,Fduring the hot weather and to be aware
OL,19,Fof the pressure facing the NHS at this
OL,20,Fbusy time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
