PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,FBetween Friday and Tuesday, the Trust
OL,7,Fsays it responded to 18,206 incidents,
OL,8,Fcompared with 14,684 during the same
OL,9,Fperiod last year - an increase of more
OL,10,Fthan 24%.
OL,12,FPeople are asked to only to call 999
OL,13,Fif it's a life-threatening emergency
OL,14,Fand to seek treatment with alternative
OL,15,Fproviders if they are facing non-life-
OL,16,Fthreatening conditions, including NHS
OL,17,F111, pharmacies, GP services, and
OL,18,Furgent treatment centres.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,FAs temperatures reach record levels
OL,7,Ffor May, the Trust also recommends
OL,8,Fpeople stay hydrated, wear sunscreen
OL,9,Fand keep in the shade from 11am to 3pm.
OL,11,FThose with elderly relatives or
OL,12,Fneighbours are being urged to check up
OL,13,Fon them regularly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
