PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,FJohn Martin, Chief Executive at
OL,7,FSWASFT, said: "We want to be there for
OL,8,Feveryone that needs us in a life-
OL,9,Fthreatening emergency; to do this, we
OL,10,Fneed to have our ambulances free to
OL,11,Frespond to those most in need. If you
OL,12,Fcall us and we're not the right
OL,13,Fservice for you, we will direct you to
OL,14,Fanother part of the NHS, please do
OL,15,Flisten to this advice, as it could
OL,16,Fmean that you get the help you need
OL,17,Fmore quickly.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,F"We are receiving calls for issues
OL,7,Fsuch as sunburn, feeling hot, and
OL,8,Fother non-emergency conditions that
OL,9,Fcan often be managed through self-
OL,10,Fcare, pharmacies, NHS 111 or other
OL,11,Fhealthcare services. Every less urgent
OL,12,F999 call reduces our ability to
OL,13,Frespond quickly to patients facing
OL,14,Flife-threatening emergencies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,F"999 should be used for serious
OL,7,Fmedical emergencies such as cardiac
OL,8,Farrest, chest pain, breathing
OL,9,Fdifficulties, suspected stroke, loss
OL,10,Fof consciousness, choking, severe
OL,11,Fallergic reactions or catastrophic
OL,12,Fbleeding."
OL,14,FDr Martin adds: "Our teams are working
OL,15,Fincredibly hard alongside NHS partners
OL,16,Fto manage these unprecedented levels
OL,17,Fof demand, and we are sorry when we
OL,18,Fcannot reach some patients as quickly
OL,19,Fas we would like.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1780081925
OL,3,CAmbulance service has busiest day on
OL,4,Crecord in heatwave
OL,6,F"Please do not call back to ask for an
OL,7,Fambulance arrival time. We are unable
OL,8,Fto provide estimated arrival times and
OL,9,Frepeat calls can delay our response to
OL,10,Fother patients needing urgent help."
OL,12,FHe continued that people should
OL,13,Fexercise extra caution when going into
OL,14,Fthe water to keep cool and ensure they
OL,15,Fare eating and drinking enough in the
OL,16,Fhot weather.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
